
'''= SCIBE explores the relationship between scarcity and creativity in the context of the built environment by investigating how conditions of scarcity might affect the creativity of the different actors''' involved in the production of architecture and urban design, and how design-led actions might improve the built environment in the future. 

URL = http://www.scibe.eu/

The research is based on the analysis of processes in four European cities: London, Oslo, Reykjavik, and Vienna.


